	(text "The LNA is powered through the RF-OUT pin. We\nAC-couple the RF-OUT pin to what we actually want to\nsend the output too, while using an inductor to\nDC-couple the pin to the voltage source while blocking\nany AC from getting to the voltage bus."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
